videos.description: Wofford moves the ball where it ends up in the hands of Nathan Hoover who bounces it to Keve Aluma for the nasty two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Hoover's dime leads to an Aluma dunk

videos.description: Off a Wofford turnover, Reggie Perry runs the floor and lays down the hammer off a Lamar Peters pass.
videos.headline: Perry destroys the rim
